            <title><![CDATA[Nintendo Switch's Latest Update Disables Popular Game-Sharing Loophole]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gamespot.com/articles/nintendo-switchs-latest-update-disables-popular-game-sharing-loophole/1100-6531301/?ftag=CAD-01-10abi2f</link>
